{"id":515,"parent_id":497,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":515,"title":"Psalm 18","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ps.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Psalm 18"],[".studySummary",["i","David praises the Lord for His greatness and preserving care—The Lord’s way is perfect—The Lord has given marvelous blessings—David testifies, The Lord lives, and blessed be my Rock."]],[".intro","To the chief Musician,",["i","A Psalm"],"of David, the servant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", who spake unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"the words of this song in the day",["i","that"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"delivered him from the hand of all his enemies, and from the hand of Saul: And he said,"]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.1","order":"02.20.018.35393"},["b","1"],"I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"love"],"thee, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", my strength."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.2","order":"02.20.018.35394"},["b","2"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"rock"],", and my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"fortress"],", and my deliverer; my God, my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"strength"],", in whom I will",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"trust"],"; my buckler, and the horn of my salvation,",["i","and"],"my high tower."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.3","order":"02.20.018.35395"},["b","3"],"I will call upon the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","who is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"worthy"]],"to be praised: so shall I be saved from mine enemies."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.4","order":"02.20.018.35396"},["b","4"],"The sorrows of death compassed me, and the floods of ungodly men made me afraid."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.5","order":"02.20.018.35397"},["b","5"],"The sorrows of hell compassed me about: the snares of death",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"prevented"],"me."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.6","order":"02.20.018.35398"},["b","6"],"In my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"distress"],"I called upon the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and cried unto my God: he heard my voice out of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"temple"],", and my cry came before him,",["i","even"],"into his ears."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.7","order":"02.20.018.35399"},["b","7"],"Then the earth shook and trembled; the foundations also of the hills moved and were shaken, because he was wroth."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.8","order":"02.20.018.35400"},["b","8"],"There went up a smoke out of his nostrils, and fire out of his mouth devoured: coals were kindled by it."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.9","order":"02.20.018.35401"},["b","9"],"He bowed the heavens also, and came down: and darkness",["i","was"],"under his feet."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.10","order":"02.20.018.35402"},["b","10"],"And he rode upon a cherub, and did fly: yea, he did fly upon the wings of the wind."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.11","order":"02.20.018.35403"},["b","11"],"He made darkness his secret place; his pavilion round about him",["i","were"],"dark waters",["i","and"],"thick clouds of the skies."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.12","order":"02.20.018.35404"},["b","12"],"At the brightness",["i","that was"],"before him his thick clouds passed, hail",["i","stones"],"and coals of fire."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.13","order":"02.20.018.35405"},["b","13"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"also thundered in the heavens, and the Highest gave his voice; hail",["i","stones"],"and coals of fire."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.14","order":"02.20.018.35406"},["b","14"],"Yea, he sent out his arrows, and scattered them; and he shot out lightnings, and discomfited them."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.15","order":"02.20.018.35407"},["b","15"],"Then the channels of waters were seen, and the foundations of the world were discovered at thy rebuke, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", at the blast of the breath of thy nostrils."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.16","order":"02.20.018.35408"},["b","16"],"He sent from above, he took me, he drew me out of many waters."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.17","order":"02.20.018.35409"},["b","17"],"He delivered me from my strong enemy, and from them which hated me: for they were too strong for me."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.18","order":"02.20.018.35410"},["b","18"],"They prevented me in the day of my calamity: but the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was my stay."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.19","order":"02.20.018.35411"},["b","19"],"He brought me forth also into a large place; he delivered me, because he delighted in me."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.20","order":"02.20.018.35412"},["b","20"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"rewarded me according to my righteousness; according to the cleanness of my hands hath he recompensed me."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.21","order":"02.20.018.35413"},["b","21"],"For I have kept the ways of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and have not wickedly departed from my God."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.22","order":"02.20.018.35414"},["b","22"],"For all his judgments",["i","were"],"before me, and I did not put away his statutes from me."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.23","order":"02.20.018.35415"},["b","23"],"I was also upright before him, and I kept myself from mine iniquity."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.24","order":"02.20.018.35416"},["b","24"],"Therefore hath the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"recompensed me according to my righteousness, according to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"cleanness"],"of my hands in his eyesight."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.25","order":"02.20.018.35417"},["b","25"],"With the merciful thou wilt shew thyself merciful; with an upright man thou wilt shew thyself upright;"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.26","order":"02.20.018.35418"},["b","26"],"With the pure thou wilt shew thyself pure; and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"with"],"the froward thou wilt shew thyself froward."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.27","order":"02.20.018.35419"},["b","27"],"For thou wilt save the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"afflicted"],"people; but wilt bring down",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"high"],"looks."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.28","order":"02.20.018.35420"},["b","28"],"For thou wilt light my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"candle"],": the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"my God will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"enlighten"],"my darkness."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.29","order":"02.20.018.35421"},["b","29"],"For by thee I have run through a troop; and by my God have I leaped over a wall."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.30","order":"02.20.018.35422"},["b","30"],["i","As for"],"God, his way",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"perfect"],": the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"word"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"is tried: he",["i","is"],"a buckler to all those that trust in him."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.31","order":"02.20.018.35423"},["b","31"],"For who",["i","is"],"God save the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"? or who",["i","is"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"rock"],"save our God?"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.32","order":"02.20.018.35424"},["b","32"],["i","It is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"God"],"that girdeth me with strength, and maketh my way perfect."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.33","order":"02.20.018.35425"},["b","33"],"He maketh my feet like hinds’",["i","feet"],["i",","],"and setteth me upon my high places."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.34","order":"02.20.018.35426"},["b","34"],"He teacheth my hands to war, so that a bow of steel is broken by mine arms."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.35","order":"02.20.018.35427"},["b","35"],"Thou hast also given me the shield of thy salvation: and thy right hand hath holden me up, and thy gentleness hath made me great."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.36","order":"02.20.018.35428"},["b","36"],"Thou hast enlarged my steps under me, that my feet did not slip."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.37","order":"02.20.018.35429"},["b","37"],"I have pursued mine enemies, and overtaken them: neither did I turn again till they were consumed."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.38","order":"02.20.018.35430"},["b","38"],"I have wounded them that they were not able to rise: they are fallen under my feet."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.39","order":"02.20.018.35431"},["b","39"],"For thou hast girded me with strength unto the battle: thou hast subdued under me those that rose up against me."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.40","order":"02.20.018.35432"},["b","40"],"Thou hast also given me the necks of mine enemies; that I might destroy them that hate me."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.41","order":"02.20.018.35433"},["b","41"],"They",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"cried"],", but",["i","there was"],"none to save",["i","them: even"],"unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", but he answered them not."],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.42","order":"02.20.018.35434"},["b","42"],"Then did I beat them small as the dust before the wind: I did cast them out as the dirt in the streets."],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.43","order":"02.20.018.35435"},["b","43"],"Thou hast delivered me from the strivings of the people;",["i","and"],"thou hast made me the head of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_43a"},"heathen"],": a people",["i","whom"],"I have not known shall serve me."],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.44","order":"02.20.018.35436"},["b","44"],"As soon as they hear of me, they shall obey me: the strangers shall submit themselves unto me."],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.45","order":"02.20.018.35437"},["b","45"],"The strangers shall fade away, and be afraid out of their close places."],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.46","order":"02.20.018.35438"},["b","46"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_46a"},"liveth"],"; and blessed",["i","be"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_46b"},"rock"],"; and let the God of my salvation be exalted."],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.47","order":"02.20.018.35439"},["b","47"],["i","It is"],"God that avengeth me, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_47a"},"subdueth"],"the people under me."],["div",{"id":"48","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.48","order":"02.20.018.35440"},["b","48"],"He delivereth me from mine enemies: yea, thou liftest me up above those that rise up against me: thou hast delivered me from the violent man."],["div",{"id":"49","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.49","order":"02.20.018.35441"},["b","49"],"Therefore will I give thanks unto thee, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_49a"},"heathen"],", and sing praises unto thy name."],["div",{"id":"50","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.50","order":"02.20.018.35442"},["b","50"],"Great deliverance giveth he to his king; and sheweth mercy to his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_50a"},"anointed"],", to David, and to his seed for evermore."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.1a","order":"02.20.018.35443"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/13.29"},"Alma 13:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.31"},"D&C 20:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.116"},"76:116"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.2a","order":"02.20.018.35445"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/comfort"},"TG Comfort"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rock"},"Rock"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.2b","order":"02.20.018.35447"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/protection-divine"},"TG Protection, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.2c","order":"02.20.018.35449"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strength"},"TG Strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.2d","order":"02.20.018.35451"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.13"},"Heb. 2:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.3a","order":"02.20.018.35453"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worthiness"},"TG Worthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.5a","order":"02.20.018.35455"},["b","5a"],["span.small","HEB"],"confronted."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.6a","order":"02.20.018.35457"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"TG Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.6b","order":"02.20.018.35459"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/2.7"},"Jonah 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.24a","order":"02.20.018.35461"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cleanliness"},"TG Cleanliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.26a","order":"02.20.018.35463"},["b","26a"],["span.small","OR"],"with the twisted thou wilt be subtle."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.27a","order":"02.20.018.35465"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/22.28"},"2 Sam. 22:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49.13"},"Isa. 49:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.13"},"1 Ne. 21:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.27b","order":"02.20.018.35467"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/20.33"},"2 Ne. 20:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/25.1"},"3 Ne. 25:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.9"},"D&C 29:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.28a","order":"02.20.018.35469"},["b","28a"],["span.small","OR"],"lamp."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.28b","order":"02.20.018.35471"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/edification"},"TG Edification"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.30a","order":"02.20.018.35473"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-perfection-of"},"TG God, Perfection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"30b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.30b","order":"02.20.018.35475"},["b","30b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/22.31"},"2 Sam. 22:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/12.6.6-7"},"Ps. 12:6 (6–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.31a","order":"02.20.018.35477"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rock"},"TG Rock"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.32a","order":"02.20.018.35479"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/7.12"},"1 Ne. 7:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.12"},"Alma 26:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"41a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.41a","order":"02.20.018.35481"},["b","41a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.11.10-11"},"Jer. 11:11 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/21.15"},"Mosiah 21:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.7"},"D&C 101:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"43a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.43a","order":"02.20.018.35483"},["b","43a"],["span.small","HEB"],"nations."],["div",{"id":"46a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.46a","order":"02.20.018.35485"},["b","46a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/5.24"},"Deut. 5:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"46b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.46b","order":"02.20.018.35487"},["b","46b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rock"},"TG Rock"],"."],["div",{"id":"47a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.47a","order":"02.20.018.35489"},["b","47a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/47.3"},"Ps. 47:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"49a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.49a","order":"02.20.018.35491"},["b","49a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.9"},"Rom. 15:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"50a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.50a","order":"02.20.018.35493"},["b","50a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/20.6"},"Ps. 20:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.80"},"D&C 109:80"],"."]]}
